 skeptisk til iberiasnegler som mat.", "- I mitt f\u00f8deland Korea spiser vi marine snegler, men ikke skall-l\u00f8se landsnegler som denne iberiasneglen, sier han. Lee ser heller ingen umiddelbar markedsmulighet for den slimete, store sneglen.", "- Vet du hva vi gj\u00f8r? Du spiser iberiasnegler, for \u00e5 sjekke hvordan de er, sier Lee. - Og s\u00e5 ringer jeg deg etter en uke, og f\u00e5r rapport. Hahaha!"]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|sortrondelag"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "6b120827bc03716f223fca1f7bfb7cbdda1f10c52f1766bb068248b7f571086a"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-05-14T07:50:07.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "I stedet for \u00e5 bare drepe iberiasneglene, b\u00f8r vi spise dem, mener NTNU-forsker."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1141738.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Dag_Dolmen"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/b1384e642988ff76beb37a50550ba0a47a4ad0d2.jpg?597fae28"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["- Spis mordersneglene! -adressa.no", "M\u00e5 t\u00f8mme tarmen"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "b1384e642988ff76beb37a50550ba0a47a4ad0d2"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "sortrondelag"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "education"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["spise iberiasnegler", "t\u00f8mme tarmen", "sneglen", "spis", "spis mordersneglene", "iberiasnegler"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["matforsk", "korea", "karin r\u00f8li og borghild melbye", "orkanger", "adresseavisen", "lee", "b\u00e5rdshau